# Per-instance Postfix overlay for mail2.test.
#
# Files placed in this directory are mounted at /etc/postfix-overlay inside
# the reference-postfix container. The image's entrypoint merges this on top
# of its baked-in main.cf / master.cf defaults at startup.
#
# Common files to drop here:
#   main.cf.d/10-relay.cf          additional Postfix parameters
#   master.cf.d/20-submission.cf   extra master.cf services
#   sql/virtual-mailbox-maps.cf    custom SQL lookup overrides
#
# Empty by default — the published reference-postfix image's defaults are
# sufficient for the standard traditional-server setup driven by env vars.
